WEBVTT

00:01:22.350 --> 00:01:26.640
The Angel Next Door
Spoils Me Rotten

00:01:31.400 --> 00:01:32.970
Amane!

00:01:32.970 --> 00:01:34.110
I know you're there!

00:01:34.110 --> 00:01:35.780
Amane!

00:01:36.390 --> 00:01:39.490
There you are, Amane. Don't you look well?

00:01:39.760 --> 00:01:43.740
Yeah, yeah. I'm very well,
so will you leave now?

00:01:44.160 --> 00:01:47.280
Wow, what a way to talk to your mother.

00:01:47.280 --> 00:01:49.930
It took me hours to come
all the way here, you know.

00:01:49.750 --> 00:01:55.750
Fujimiya

00:01:49.930 --> 00:01:51.420
Show a little appreciation!

00:01:51.930 --> 00:01:55.760
Thank you very much for
traveling such a long distance.

00:01:57.330 --> 00:01:58.260
Now leave.

00:01:58.690 --> 00:01:59.990
My!

00:01:59.990 --> 00:02:03.520
Unlike Shuto-san, you have
absolutely no charm.

00:02:03.520 --> 00:02:05.770
Guys don't need charm anyway.

00:02:06.340 --> 00:02:08.200
A rebellious phase, huh?

00:02:08.200 --> 00:02:09.900
Well then, please excuse me.

00:02:09.900 --> 00:02:10.990
Wait a second.

00:02:10.990 --> 00:02:12.020
Nobody said...

00:02:12.350 --> 00:02:16.280
You realize Shuto-san's and my income
is what pays the rent here?

00:02:19.530 --> 00:02:24.030
Fujimiya

00:02:19.970 --> 00:02:21.980
Excuse me, please.

00:02:24.030 --> 00:02:29.040
Reward for the Angel

00:02:32.120 --> 00:02:34.040
Listen, Mom.

00:02:34.040 --> 00:02:37.300
If you're coming over, at least
tell me first. Like an adult.

00:02:37.820 --> 00:02:41.550
I have to catch you off guard to make sure
you're actually taking care of yourself.

00:02:43.190 --> 00:02:45.240
B-But I'm okay, right?

00:02:45.710 --> 00:02:47.210
The place is clean, too.

00:02:47.210 --> 00:02:50.550
It sure is. What a surprise.
Very unexpected.

00:02:50.550 --> 00:02:53.730
And your skin is glowing, so you
must be getting enough nutrition.

00:02:54.270 --> 00:02:55.730
Y-Yeah.

00:02:56.960 --> 00:02:58.120
Oh, no.

00:02:59.780 --> 00:03:02.520
Amane! I know you're there!

00:03:01.480 --> 00:03:04.860
Sorry! Will you go to my
room for a while? Please.

00:03:03.320 --> 00:03:04.860
Amane!

00:03:05.320 --> 00:03:06.920
Amane!

00:03:05.660 --> 00:03:07.590
O-Okay.

00:03:07.880 --> 00:03:09.430
Amane!

00:03:07.880 --> 00:03:11.000
Also, I'll give you this.

00:03:09.430 --> 00:03:11.000
Amane! I know you can hear me!

00:03:11.600 --> 00:03:14.670
I'll find a way to drag my mom outside.

00:03:12.120 --> 00:03:13.750
Amane!

00:03:14.140 --> 00:03:17.250
Hurry and open up! Amane?

00:03:14.670 --> 00:03:17.250
When I do, go back to your place.

00:03:17.940 --> 00:03:20.480
It looks like you've been cooking, too.

00:03:20.480 --> 00:03:23.660
Oh? Dishes for two?

00:03:24.360 --> 00:03:26.380
Yeah, I had a friend over.

00:03:26.380 --> 00:03:27.670
Hmm...

00:03:28.750 --> 00:03:30.770
Maybe I'll check your bedroom next.

00:03:31.830 --> 00:03:34.770
I know you're my mother, but I prefer
to keep my bedroom private.

00:03:34.770 --> 00:03:37.710
Oh, yeah? Do you have something
embarrassing in there?

00:03:37.710 --> 00:03:39.050
Think about it.

00:03:39.050 --> 00:03:41.180
A high school boy is
going to have one or two

00:03:41.180 --> 00:03:42.530
embarrassing things in his bedroom!

00:03:44.070 --> 00:03:44.990
Amane.

00:03:45.350 --> 00:03:46.660
Y-Yes?

00:03:47.430 --> 00:03:49.160
What are you hiding from me?

00:03:50.470 --> 00:03:52.540
It's none of your business, Mom.

00:03:54.050 --> 00:03:56.060
Of course you'd say something like that.

00:03:56.060 --> 00:03:57.040
In that case...

00:04:02.700 --> 00:04:03.260
Huh?

00:04:18.920 --> 00:04:21.070
Amane! You little devil, you!

00:04:21.490 --> 00:04:24.280
You've got such an adorable girlfriend!

00:04:24.280 --> 00:04:26.200
I can't leave you alone for a second!

00:04:26.510 --> 00:04:29.620
N-No way! She isn't
my girlfriend or anything!

00:04:30.600 --> 00:04:33.580
Oh, my. You don't need to make excuses to me!

00:04:33.580 --> 00:04:37.290
As your mother, I'll support
anyone you choose, Amane.

00:04:37.290 --> 00:04:38.600
But you're getting it—

00:04:38.600 --> 00:04:40.190
Wrong? How?

00:04:40.190 --> 00:04:44.220
You wouldn't invite a girl
over unless you liked her.

00:04:44.760 --> 00:04:49.220
And a girl wouldn't go in a boy's
room unless she liked him, too.

00:04:51.420 --> 00:04:54.730
Well, I guess I do like her.

00:04:56.740 --> 00:04:59.000
I like her as a friend.

00:04:59.000 --> 00:05:02.230
Don't try to turn all opposite-sex
friendships into something romantic.

00:05:02.670 --> 00:05:06.090
I know she doesn't
think of it that way either.

00:05:06.090 --> 00:05:07.110
If you get the wrong idea—

00:05:07.110 --> 00:05:08.010
Oh.

00:05:08.760 --> 00:05:09.530
Hmm?

00:05:16.440 --> 00:05:18.670
Sh-Shiina.

00:05:18.670 --> 00:05:21.210
There's been a misunderstanding.
Could you help me explain?

00:05:21.860 --> 00:05:23.390
Misunderstanding?

00:05:23.390 --> 00:05:26.160
Hey, hey, Miss Girlfriend. What's your name?

00:05:26.160 --> 00:05:27.090
Huh?!

00:05:27.090 --> 00:05:30.360
U-Um, I'm Mahiru Shiina.

00:05:30.360 --> 00:05:33.710
Aww, Mahiru-chan? What an adorable name!

00:05:33.710 --> 00:05:36.770
I'm Shihoko. Feel free
to call me by my first name, too.

00:05:37.200 --> 00:05:39.190
S-Sure.

00:05:47.040 --> 00:05:49.480
U-Um, Amane's Mother...

00:05:49.480 --> 00:05:52.830
Oh, my! You accept me as a mother already?

00:05:52.830 --> 00:05:54.080
Fujimiya-san!

00:05:54.080 --> 00:05:56.460
"Fujimiya" could mean me or Amane.

00:05:56.460 --> 00:05:57.540
Right, Amane?

00:05:57.900 --> 00:06:01.880
Eh? Mom, you're making Shiina nervous.

00:06:02.360 --> 00:06:04.000
Amane.

00:06:04.000 --> 00:06:07.300
You have to call your girlfriend
by her first name, you know.

00:06:07.790 --> 00:06:10.640
U-Um, Shihoko-san?

00:06:10.640 --> 00:06:11.590
What, darling?

00:06:12.060 --> 00:06:13.600
Fujimiya-san and I—

00:06:13.600 --> 00:06:15.520
But which one do you mean?

00:06:17.120 --> 00:06:20.620
A-Amane-kun and I don't have
that kind of relationship.

00:06:20.620 --> 00:06:23.360
Oh, dear! So I guess
things are still developing!

00:06:23.360 --> 00:06:27.080
Huh? Um, that isn't what I...

00:06:27.080 --> 00:06:29.080
Oh, silly me!

00:06:29.080 --> 00:06:31.780
Did I accidentally spoil the mood here?

00:06:32.700 --> 00:06:34.480
U-Um...

00:06:34.480 --> 00:06:37.120
I must insist that you allow me to explain!

00:06:37.120 --> 00:06:38.120
Yes, ma'am.

00:06:38.400 --> 00:06:43.310
Amane... kun lets me eat dinner with him.

00:06:43.310 --> 00:06:45.900
Amane-kun can't cook for himself, so...

00:06:46.800 --> 00:06:51.220
If that's why, then I'd love for you
to keep supporting him, Mahiru-chan!

00:06:51.520 --> 00:06:53.560
N-No, I mean...

00:06:55.360 --> 00:06:57.350
Give it up, Shiina.

00:06:57.840 --> 00:07:00.770
Once Mom gets worked up, she stops listening.

00:07:01.340 --> 00:07:03.270
Oh, no!

00:07:05.970 --> 00:07:07.150
Really?

00:07:07.610 --> 00:07:10.310
Not just cooking, but cleaning, too?

00:07:11.240 --> 00:07:13.240
Does that mean you two are living together?

00:07:14.820 --> 00:07:16.640
How did you come up with that?!

00:07:16.640 --> 00:07:18.080
She lives next door!

00:07:18.080 --> 00:07:21.230
Oh, my. So you were destined to meet!

00:07:21.230 --> 00:07:23.480
I'm so happy for you, Amane!

00:07:23.480 --> 00:07:26.960
Such a beautiful and well-rounded girl
tending to your every need!

00:07:27.390 --> 00:07:31.380
I don't deny that she's beautiful
and classy, but "destined to meet"?!

00:07:31.380 --> 00:07:35.470
Mahiru-chan, as a parent
I may not be perfectly objective,

00:07:35.990 --> 00:07:39.260
but while Amane has a mouth on him
and is pretty stubborn,

00:07:39.260 --> 00:07:41.530
he can still be sincere and gentlemanly,

00:07:41.530 --> 00:07:44.430
so I think it's fair to say
you scored a real prize.

00:07:44.430 --> 00:07:45.980
O-Oh.

00:07:46.660 --> 00:07:49.370
Well, he does have
zero experience with girls,

00:07:49.370 --> 00:07:52.530
so it's probably best if you
take the reins there, Mahiru-chan.

00:07:53.040 --> 00:07:55.240
Mom, what are you talking about?!
Seriously, shut up!

00:07:55.850 --> 00:07:57.340
Just go home already!

00:07:59.320 --> 00:08:01.150
Well, if you insist.

00:08:01.540 --> 00:08:03.100
All right, then.

00:08:03.550 --> 00:08:07.210
I did spoil your special time
with your girlfriend, after all.

00:08:07.210 --> 00:08:09.510
Oh. Mahiru-chan?

00:08:09.510 --> 00:08:11.630
Huh? Y-Yes?

00:08:12.610 --> 00:08:15.130
Mahiru-chan, will you give me
your contact info?

00:08:15.130 --> 00:08:16.460
O-Okay.

00:08:20.160 --> 00:08:21.740
That was exhausting.

00:08:21.740 --> 00:08:25.160
Sorry. I sent her home
without clearing anything up.

00:08:25.160 --> 00:08:28.230
It's all right. There's no real harm.

00:08:29.110 --> 00:08:31.520
I wouldn't be so sure.

00:08:31.520 --> 00:08:34.880
It looked like she really liked you, Shiina.

00:08:34.880 --> 00:08:36.780
She'll probably keep bugging you.

00:08:36.780 --> 00:08:41.790
Shihoko-san really does think the world
of you, doesn't she, Fujimiya-san?

00:08:44.530 --> 00:08:45.540
That must be nice.

00:08:46.440 --> 00:08:47.950
What's nice about it?

00:08:47.950 --> 00:08:51.850
Your mother.
She's really bubbly, but she's kind.

00:08:51.850 --> 00:08:54.960
More like nosy and annoying!

00:08:54.960 --> 00:08:57.450
It still seems nice, though.

00:09:05.490 --> 00:09:07.560
"Mahiru-chan," huh?

00:09:08.110 --> 00:09:09.680
What is it now?

00:09:09.680 --> 00:09:13.960
Oh, it's been a while since someone's
called me by my own name.

00:09:13.960 --> 00:09:15.920
It's always my last name.

00:09:15.920 --> 00:09:20.080
Well, if you don't have friends who are
that close, then probably just your parents.

00:09:21.900 --> 00:09:24.950
My parents would never call me
by my name. Ever.

00:09:27.060 --> 00:09:29.630
Anyway, it's just unusual for me.

00:09:33.400 --> 00:09:34.440
Mahiru.

00:09:41.880 --> 00:09:44.770
It's not hard to get someone
to call you by your name.

00:09:48.950 --> 00:09:50.520
I guess that's true.

00:09:53.520 --> 00:09:54.650
Amane-kun.

00:09:56.560 --> 00:09:58.780
Just don't call me that in public, okay?

00:09:59.520 --> 00:10:01.690
You don't have to tell me!

00:10:01.690 --> 00:10:04.520
You, too. Don't let it slip
in front of people.

00:10:04.520 --> 00:10:08.460
I understand. It'll be our secret, right?

00:10:08.460 --> 00:10:09.210
Yeah.

00:10:09.640 --> 00:10:10.380
Oh.

00:10:11.280 --> 00:10:13.050
I should return your key.

00:10:13.600 --> 00:10:16.110
I don't mind if you keep it for a while.

00:10:16.110 --> 00:10:16.860
Huh?

00:10:17.420 --> 00:10:20.280
You can just give it back when
we stop hanging out.

00:10:20.280 --> 00:10:21.350
Yeah, but...

00:10:21.970 --> 00:10:24.850
It's a pain to have
to go to the door every time.

00:10:25.340 --> 00:10:27.230
Your true intentions are showing.

00:10:27.610 --> 00:10:30.890
Don't you get tired of using
the intercom and waiting?

00:10:30.890 --> 00:10:34.820
Even if I did, you're making
a very incautious decision.

00:10:35.680 --> 00:10:38.490
I'm lending it to you
because I trust you.

00:10:46.820 --> 00:10:50.180
All right, then. I'll borrow it.

00:10:51.880 --> 00:10:54.460
Just don't blame me if something
happens to your place, okay?

00:10:54.810 --> 00:10:55.840
Like what?

00:10:56.470 --> 00:10:59.470
Like you find the entire room
cleaned without your knowledge.

00:10:59.470 --> 00:11:00.720
I'd appreciate that!

00:11:01.050 --> 00:11:04.410
Or you find your fridge stuffed
with ready-to-eat meals!

00:11:04.410 --> 00:11:06.590
I'd be so happy at breakfast!

00:11:06.590 --> 00:11:08.750
Are you trying to make fun of me?

00:11:08.750 --> 00:11:09.990
Not one bit.

