00:11:57.240 --> 00:11:58.390
Not especially.

00:11:58.800 --> 00:12:00.030
I bought that for you.

00:12:00.350 --> 00:12:02.650
Huh? Why?

00:12:03.180 --> 00:12:05.240
You're at the top of the class.

00:12:05.640 --> 00:12:07.580
That deserves a little celebration.

00:12:08.040 --> 00:12:09.420
Congratulations on first place.

00:12:11.580 --> 00:12:16.270
But I always get first place,
so I don't think it's that special.

00:12:16.270 --> 00:12:18.670
Yeah, but you still always work really hard.

00:12:18.670 --> 00:12:21.580
Why not accept a little reward for once?

00:12:24.280 --> 00:12:25.660
A reward...

00:12:38.820 --> 00:12:40.580
Yeah. Congrats.

00:12:40.990 --> 00:12:42.920
Thank you. I appreciate it.

00:12:56.660 --> 00:12:58.310
Is something wrong?

00:12:59.110 --> 00:13:00.670
No, it's nothing.

00:13:01.590 --> 00:13:02.460
Oh.

00:13:06.370 --> 00:13:07.300
Wha—

00:13:07.900 --> 00:13:11.560
N-No, I didn't mean I wanted some.

00:13:12.000 --> 00:13:13.230
Oh, you didn't?

00:13:13.630 --> 00:13:16.810
I'll take it if you're offering, of course.

00:13:17.130 --> 00:13:20.270
You're the one who bought it
in the first place, Amane-kun,

00:13:20.270 --> 00:13:22.980
so I think you have every right to eat some.

00:13:30.360 --> 00:13:31.390
It's so sweet!

00:13:31.390 --> 00:13:32.990
Well, it is cake.

00:13:34.960 --> 00:13:36.500
Give it here.

00:13:40.150 --> 00:13:40.940
I'm, uh...

00:13:40.940 --> 00:13:41.830
Eat.

00:13:56.160 --> 00:13:58.160
So? How was that?

00:13:58.160 --> 00:14:00.200
D-Delicious.

00:14:00.200 --> 00:14:03.190
No. I mean being fed like that.

00:14:03.890 --> 00:14:06.950
It was entirely unbearable.

00:14:07.540 --> 00:14:08.880
I thought so.

00:14:08.880 --> 00:14:11.420
If you do stuff like this,
people get the wrong idea.

00:14:14.770 --> 00:14:17.540
I've got to keep my guard up, too.

00:14:23.430 --> 00:14:26.840
I thought I'd try making lunches by myself,

00:14:27.810 --> 00:14:31.160
but I'm so used to Mahiru's
fantastic cooking now,

00:14:31.160 --> 00:14:34.540
I'm not sure I'll even
be able to finish my own.

00:14:36.960 --> 00:14:40.600
Yeah, seriously.
Mahiru is spoiling me rotten.

00:14:46.070 --> 00:14:46.900
Oh.

00:14:47.520 --> 00:14:49.400
Were you shopping, too, Amane-kun?

00:14:50.000 --> 00:14:51.740
Well, sorta.

00:14:57.940 --> 00:15:00.510
But shouldn't you let me handle that?

00:15:00.510 --> 00:15:01.130
Huh?

00:15:01.580 --> 00:15:06.200
Amane-kun, are you confident
you won't make a mess of your kitchen?

00:15:05.040 --> 00:15:07.840
Fujimiya

00:15:07.040 --> 00:15:07.840
Not a bit.

00:15:08.560 --> 00:15:12.150
Then it might be best if I
were to supervise things.

00:15:14.120 --> 00:15:16.850
So you've decided on the menu?

00:15:17.330 --> 00:15:19.240
Sautéed vegetables and omelettes.

00:15:19.240 --> 00:15:21.230
Are you seasoning the vegetables?

00:15:21.600 --> 00:15:24.610
Yeah. Gonna douse 'em with yakiniku sauce.

00:15:26.690 --> 00:15:28.890
Quite a bold flavor, then.

00:15:39.030 --> 00:15:41.930
Taste it! Please!

00:15:42.980 --> 00:15:44.380
Thank you for the food.

00:15:51.300 --> 00:15:54.330
It's just bland scrambled eggs.

00:15:54.330 --> 00:15:56.880
You didn't add any salt or pepper, did you?

00:15:56.880 --> 00:15:59.710
Ah... I completely forgot.

00:15:59.710 --> 00:16:02.010
And it was supposed to be an omelette, too.

00:16:02.010 --> 00:16:03.980
You stirred the eggs too much.

00:16:03.980 --> 00:16:07.520
What did you think would happen
if you scrambled them like that?

00:16:07.520 --> 00:16:08.900
I even warned you.

00:16:09.510 --> 00:16:10.730
I'm sorry!

00:16:13.840 --> 00:16:16.490
Why don't you try the one I made as a sample?

00:16:17.220 --> 00:16:19.300
Please eat it before it gets cold.

00:16:20.260 --> 00:16:21.000
Thanks.

00:16:26.640 --> 00:16:29.580
I think you did the best
you could, Amane-kun.

00:16:30.000 --> 00:16:32.700
The important part is
having a desire to cook.

00:16:33.240 --> 00:16:37.480
But if you ever reached the point
where you could cook well by yourself,

00:16:37.480 --> 00:16:39.560
I wonder if my services
would no longer be needed.

00:16:40.010 --> 00:16:42.230
No! I mean, I...

00:16:42.230 --> 00:16:45.270
I want to keep eating your cooking, Mahiru!

00:16:47.000 --> 00:16:49.850
Though I know how pathetic
and presumptuous that sounds...

00:16:52.900 --> 00:16:54.780
What am I going to do with you?

00:16:55.240 --> 00:16:59.160
I don't plan to quit any time soon,
so I think you can relax.

00:17:00.930 --> 00:17:01.910
Thank you.

00:17:02.350 --> 00:17:05.550
Maybe I'll have you help out
from time to time.

00:17:05.550 --> 00:17:07.300
Peeling vegetables and stuff.

00:17:07.300 --> 00:17:09.420
But that's a job for a kid.

00:17:09.840 --> 00:17:12.570
We have to start you off small, Amane-kun.

00:17:18.830 --> 00:17:19.950
Hey, Amane!

00:17:19.180 --> 00:17:22.560
With authentic flavors...

00:17:19.180 --> 00:17:22.680
Xmas Party Set

00:17:19.950 --> 00:17:21.710
Christmas party at your place?

00:17:21.710 --> 00:17:22.180
No way.

00:17:22.180 --> 00:17:25.640
Aww! Why not? I know you'll be alo—

00:17:26.430 --> 00:17:29.860
Is it your girlfriend?!
The one you bought the presents for?!

00:17:29.860 --> 00:17:33.990
Hell no. I don't have a girlfriend.

00:17:34.320 --> 00:17:35.800
Huh?

00:17:35.800 --> 00:17:39.660
But would you really give a stuffed
animal to a casual acquaintance?

00:17:41.620 --> 00:17:43.240
To my neighbor, yeah.

00:17:43.940 --> 00:17:46.290
She shares food and helps me out with stuff.

00:17:46.600 --> 00:17:49.500
No wonder your complexion
is so much better recently.

00:17:49.790 --> 00:17:53.370
If there's no girlfriend, then why not?
Let's have a Christmas party at your place!

00:17:53.370 --> 00:17:56.200
If you don't want to, it's fine with us.

00:17:56.200 --> 00:17:57.430
Hmm...

00:17:57.430 --> 00:17:59.030
Hmm?

00:17:59.980 --> 00:18:01.320
Hmm...

00:18:01.940 --> 00:18:03.690
Fine, then.

00:18:03.690 --> 00:18:05.310
The 24th, right?

00:18:05.310 --> 00:18:07.770
We can wrap up before dinner anyway.

00:18:07.770 --> 00:18:09.310
As long as we finish by then.

00:18:11.360 --> 00:18:14.940
Ya win. I guess I gotta play along.

00:18:16.360 --> 00:18:19.880
Ao ao ao! Tha hurrs!

00:18:16.840 --> 00:18:18.640
Don't be so full of yourself!

00:18:19.880 --> 00:18:23.580
Ikkun, Awane-kun ullying ee!

00:18:22.080 --> 00:18:24.200
Hold it, Amane.

00:18:23.580 --> 00:18:26.940
Is this the mouth those words
came out of? Huh? Is it?

00:18:24.200 --> 00:18:26.090
Quit picking on Chi.

00:18:26.090 --> 00:18:28.580
I'm the only one who can pinch those cheeks!

00:18:28.960 --> 00:18:32.960
Fine, fine. Then squeeze them
real good for me.

00:18:32.960 --> 00:18:34.340
I can handle that.

00:18:35.060 --> 00:18:38.590
It's not fair if he makes you do it! Aww!

00:18:36.600 --> 00:18:40.100
Squishy squishy squishy!

00:18:38.960 --> 00:18:41.160
Staaahp!

00:18:40.100 --> 00:18:42.730
You're such a cutie!

00:18:41.160 --> 00:18:42.950
Can I leave now?

00:18:44.040 --> 00:18:46.100
Plans for Christmas?

00:18:46.660 --> 00:18:48.240
Nothing in particular.

00:18:48.240 --> 00:18:49.630
Oh, really?

00:18:49.630 --> 00:18:51.740
I was sure you'd have
a girls' night or something.

00:18:51.740 --> 00:18:56.010
Most of the classmates
I keep in touch with have boyfriends,

00:18:56.010 --> 00:18:59.440
and I turned down
all the boys who invited me out.

00:18:59.440 --> 00:19:01.580
I'll be free one way or another.

00:19:02.010 --> 00:19:03.740
I bet those boys are all in tears now.

00:19:04.230 --> 00:19:09.340
But if you're asking me about Christmas
plans, does that mean you have some?

00:19:09.340 --> 00:19:10.110
Hmm?

00:19:10.880 --> 00:19:15.500
Yeah, Itsuki is coming over
on the afternoon of the 24th.

00:19:15.880 --> 00:19:17.070
Itsuki?

00:19:17.070 --> 00:19:18.480
He's my buddy.

00:19:18.480 --> 00:19:20.070
His girlfriend's coming, too.

00:19:20.540 --> 00:19:25.470
I understand. Let me know when
your Christmas party is over, then.

00:19:25.470 --> 00:19:27.930
Okay. Sorry about this.

00:19:27.930 --> 00:19:30.190
It's fine. I hope you have fun.

00:19:35.560 --> 00:19:37.000
Won't you be lonely?

00:19:38.550 --> 00:19:39.690
I'm used to it.

00:19:40.790 --> 00:19:41.950
Being alone.

00:19:45.940 --> 00:19:48.300
Ah, actually...

00:19:50.550 --> 00:19:53.710
I realize this may sound presumptuous,

00:19:54.190 --> 00:19:58.460
but while Christmas Eve might not work,
how about spending Christmas together?

00:19:59.940 --> 00:20:02.720
Spend it together doing what?

00:20:02.720 --> 00:20:05.260
Huh? Uh...

00:20:05.260 --> 00:20:08.970
I guess there's really nothing to do. Sorry.

00:20:08.970 --> 00:20:09.770
Then...

00:20:09.770 --> 00:20:10.730
Huh?

00:20:11.320 --> 00:20:13.210
I want to try that thing.

00:20:13.210 --> 00:20:14.230
That thing?

00:20:14.920 --> 00:20:17.730
I've never played one of those before.

00:20:19.240 --> 00:20:21.740
Is that okay? Just playing games and stuff?

00:20:22.270 --> 00:20:24.780
Yes, that sounds good.

00:20:28.200 --> 00:20:30.600
Merry Christmas!

00:20:31.700 --> 00:20:34.880
Still, you sure cleaned up around here.

00:20:34.880 --> 00:20:36.750
It was pretty gnarly for a while.

00:20:36.750 --> 00:20:40.260
Mm-hmm. And it seems
to have a feminine touch.

00:20:41.240 --> 00:20:44.510
Why would you say that? More importantly,

00:20:45.490 --> 00:20:47.470
don't snuggle so much
at someone else's place!

00:20:47.470 --> 00:20:49.010
You jealous, man?

00:20:49.010 --> 00:20:50.270
Not particularly.

00:20:50.760 --> 00:20:54.020
I wonder if everyone else
is snuggled up like this, too.

00:20:54.020 --> 00:20:57.770
Don't forget the guys who are
crying tears of blood tonight.

00:20:58.320 --> 00:21:00.490
Oh, yeah. A while ago,

00:21:00.490 --> 00:21:06.710
a bunch of boys ganged up together
to try to ask the angel out on Christmas...

00:21:06.710 --> 00:21:08.550
If you please!

00:21:08.550 --> 00:21:09.740
I'm very sorry.

00:21:12.160 --> 00:21:14.790
...and she shot them all down at once.

00:21:15.540 --> 00:21:19.540
She said, "I can't because I have plans
with someone else," or something.

00:21:20.070 --> 00:21:21.050
Huh.

00:21:21.460 --> 00:21:24.700
You really don't care about
the angel at all, do you, Amane?

00:21:25.130 --> 00:21:28.550
Is it because your neighbor's
the real angel to you?

00:21:29.300 --> 00:21:30.310
Wanna get kicked out?

00:21:30.670 --> 00:21:32.310
Oh noes!

00:21:33.640 --> 00:21:35.310
Ikkun, look! It's snowing!

00:21:35.310 --> 00:21:38.540
Whoa! We're getting a real white Christmas!

00:21:38.540 --> 00:21:40.570
Hey, hey, Ikkun! Let's go out on the balcony!

00:21:40.570 --> 00:21:41.100
Yeah!

00:21:41.100 --> 00:21:43.070
White Christmas!

00:21:44.200 --> 00:21:45.770
First snow of the season.

00:21:46.370 --> 00:21:48.480
Huh?! Wha—?! What are you doing here?!

00:21:48.480 --> 00:21:50.330
What? Whaaat?!?

00:21:51.700 --> 00:21:52.580
Ma...

00:21:55.580 --> 00:21:57.580
Uh...

00:21:58.820 --> 00:21:59.550
Oh.

00:23:34.930 --> 00:23:39.930
Next Time
